In essence, the limitation means that if the ministry buys under an auction, it will impose a surcharge on the gold parachute, if they do not retire the bank director.
At the time of the direct purchase of disproportionate credits, the government will intervene aggressively to ensure that the directors’ money is not exaggerated.
In addition, the existing gold parachute contracts will not change, the limitation is valid only for new ones to encourage participation in the program.
